sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API Server
    participant Webhook Server
    participant Unitset Controller
    participant Scheduler

    User->>API Server: Create UnitSet
    API Server-->>User: Confirm creation

    API Server->>Webhook Server: Mutate/Validate UnitSet
    Note over Webhook Server: Defaulting adds finalizers:<br/>FinalizerUnitDelete<br/>FinalizerConfigMapDelete
    Webhook Server-->>API Server: Admission allowed

    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Watch UnitSet changes
    API Server-->>Unitset Controller: Notify new UnitSet

    alt Deletion in progress
        Unitset Controller->>Unitset Controller: Handle finalizers (delete Units, ConfigMaps)
    end

    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Create ConfigMap (config template)
    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Get/Copy PodTemplate from template in upm-system namespace

    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Create Headless Service
    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Create External Service (optional)
    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Create Unit Services (optional)

    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Create Unit Certificates (optional)

    Unitset Controller->>Unitset Controller: Reconcile UnitSet status

    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Create Units
    Note over API Server: UnitSet owns Units via OwnerReference

    Unitset Controller->>Unitset Controller: Patch NodeNameMap annotation

    alt PodMonitor enabled
        Unitset Controller->>API Server: Create PodMonitor
    end

    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Sync image version to Units
    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Sync resources to Units
    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Sync ResizePolicy to Units
    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Sync labels/annotations to Units
    Unitset Controller->>API Server: Sync storage/PVC to Units

    Unitset Controller->>Unitset Controller: Final UnitSet status update

    Note over Scheduler: Scheduler watches unscheduled Pods
    Scheduler->>API Server: Assign nodes to Pods
